{"about_the_game":"<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the Game</h2></strong><br>You are a product of artificial intelligence created to take part in an experiment on &quot;self-awareness&quot;. In your bid to escape, you arrive at the ends of the world. Right when you think you have evaded capture and escaped the clutches of AI, you discover that everything you have been through is all just a lie.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/\u5267\u60c5.gif?t=1727058684\" /><br><br>&quot;The Fight of Escaper&quot; is a Roguelike shooter game with cyberpunk aesthetics. You can choose from 1 male character and 2 female characters whose bodies and weapons have been cybernetically enhanced. They possess combat skills and abilities superior to those of robots.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/\u7537\u4e3b\u6280\u80fd.gif?t=1727058684\" /><br><br>In the cyber world, there are hundreds of plugin items that can be used to enhance AI. These items are not just combat weapons, they are also essential in developing unique, personalized combat tactics. Strategically choosing the right combo of items to enhance your body will enable you to surpass and dominate AI in combat.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/\u98de\u59296\u79d2\u539f\u89c6\u9891\u6587\u4ef6.gif?t=1727058684\" /><br><br>In addition to these plugin items, there is vast potential for body customization. Combining various weapons, module abilities, talents, databases and outfits will allow for a thrilling combat experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u3010Game Features\u3011</strong></h2><br>\u2605\u2605\u2605A huge variety of cyberpunk-style maps and scenes create an immersive gameplay experience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/\u573a\u666f.gif?t=1727058684\" /><br><br>\u2605\u2605\u2605Equip your protagonist with exclusive skills and stylish outfits, expanding the variety of options for both solo and team combat.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/\u5927\u5c0f\u6d4b\u8bd52\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1727058684\" /><br><br>\u2605\u2605\u2605Experience the thrill of growth as you try out different builds with each death and revival that you go through.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/\u62fe\u53d6\u82af\u7247\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1727058684\" /><br><br>\u2605\u2605\u2605The combination of hardcore mecha bosses and manic shooter mechanics makes for a challenging yet rewarding combat experience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097050/extras/BOSS\u7ea2\u5149\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1727058684\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u87b3\u8782\u6355\u8749","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1097050/21bb2a7b25dfc207ad2959554f31069643298bd3.jpg"},{"name":"\u4e00\u4e1d\u5149\u4eae","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1097050/ebcccd8dee76b54591a28641537b47bb295d3107.jpg"},{"name":"\u9a84\u50b2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1097050/7a6671d0181d5a748056dd958eaaa0535a6a3686.jpg"},{"name":"\u6210\u957f","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1097050/4cdcdaee561dda1cb3de69fb5694aa4630300793.jpg"},{"name":"\u653b\u5b88\u4e92\u6362","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1097050/26f54647ea7b05b5d99dd858bea016fe8a5a3454.jpg"},{"name":"\u6b66\u88c5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1097050/fd88a0136510284